    <div class="container vertical-spacing">
        <h1>Features</h1><br>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Privacy and security By encrypting data in motion and at rest, the DMS enterprise-class architecture ensures the confidentiality of user and company data.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Deployment and maintenance are simple. The architecture of the DMS allows for quick deployment, management, and maintenance without the need for additional resources. Self-installation and configuration modules are built in for easy deployment.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Long-term viability So that businesses can be assured that their investments will meet future needs as well as current short-term requirements, while also ensuring long-term stability and growth.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Engine of Notification Users and administrators will receive email alerts.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">DMS is simple to integrate with ERP systems like Microsoft, SAP, Oracle, and any other business technology.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Most file types that can be converted to pdf can be displayed (previewed) in advance using our solution. At an additional fee of web driver, we may additionally provide the ability to change autocad files in a web browser.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">The Repository folder's physical storage location Administrators can now explore and pick storage locations from anywhere on the network, allowing them to store data across several servers.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Backup and recovery of databases and repositories DMS Admin can backup the Database and Repository in full or selectively to another media. Our database supports distributed clustering and can self-replicate across several machines in real time, ensuring that no data is lost.</p></div>
        <div class="bullet-points"><p><i class="fa fa-check-circle-o bullet-right-spacing"></i></p><p class="text-justify">Interoperability with current systems DMS integrates effortlessly with existing systems to enhance and extend their capabilities while minimising performance effect.</p></div>
    </div>
</section>

